3011/4011 PATTERN
=================

Similar to 4710
All Horiz start in R1 phase i.e. end at R3 boundry so that fast binning can be done 
between R1/R3.


PDT is used to generate delay for better hole transport in BIs (set to min for FI).
VS-st and VS-all are the same (non-FT).
